Added the cache clearing. It is absolutely necessary, because `pwd-&gt;pw_name` may point to a static area. `getpwuid` can overwrite its contents if it fails or simply when executed somewhere else in the program.

Also removed `strdup`. Since the output of `getgrgid` and `getpwuid` [should not be freed][4], there is no need to require `free` for our wrapper functions.


